Here are some useful links to the Coinbase API / developer documentation:

* Data API: [https://www.coinbase.com/developer-platform/products/data-api](https://www.coinbase.com/developer-platform/products/data-api) ([Coinbase][1])
* Exchange API (for trading / market data): [https://www.coinbase.com/developer-platform/products/exchange-api](https://www.coinbase.com/developer-platform/products/exchange-api) ([Coinbase][2])
* CDP API (on-chain / business APIs): [https://docs.cdp.coinbase.com/api/docs/welcome](https://docs.cdp.coinbase.com/api/docs/welcome) ([Coinbase Developer Docs][3])


